ay to add a little motion and excitement to a page. You definitely don't want to overdo it, though…","fields":{"date":"2024-01-20T17:02:50.298Z","slug":"/blog/pausing-css-animations-on-hover/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Pausing CSS Animations on Hover","subtitle":"Without Any JavaScript","tags":["CSS","Animation"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/def91/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/df91e/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.jpg 131w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/9a46b/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.jpg 263w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/def91/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.jpg 525w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/2437e/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.jpg 1050w","sizes":"(min-width: 525px) 525px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/1b701/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.webp 131w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/90103/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.webp 263w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/a7b62/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.webp 525w,\n/static/d3bd4a8a2786e50282276c1a3968821d/25270/erwan-hesry-IqB5MPcQp6k-unsplash.webp 1050w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 525px) 525px, 100vw"}]},"width":525,"height":350}}}}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}